name: Pepe on Memeland
description: In Memeland, chaos erupted as Shiba, Doge, and Floki fought over which meme coin should rule. Just when all hope seemed lost, CZ Doge strolled in, munching on broccoli like it was the key to crypto wisdom. “Why not POM?” he barked. King Pepe nodded. “POM—Power of Memes! The one coin to unite them all!” And just like that, Memeland had its currency. Memes thrived, degens rejoiced, and CZ Doge kept crunching his broccoli—forever bullish on POM.
